Package com.hexaware.model

Class Payroll

java.lang.Object
com.hexaware.model.Payroll
public class Payroll extends Object
Class Payroll Represents a payroll entry for an employee. Encapsulates attributes such as payroll ID, employee ID, pay period start date, pay period end date, basic salary, overtime pay, deductions, and net salary. Provides methods to set and retrieve payroll information.
